Buffalo Cauliflower Burger

35 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten (if using regular breadcrumbs)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

SpicyComfort FoodEasy Meal

Description

A spicy, crispy cauliflower patty served on a bun with fresh toppings and a creamy sauce.

Ingredients

  • cauliflower: 1 large head
  • panko breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • buffalo sauce: 1/2 cup
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • blue cheese dressing: 1/2 cup
